quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  21,45,"Vuga uti:- jewe ndiko ndabatuza kumajambo y’ubutumwa bw’Imana, rero intumva ntizumva ubutumwa naho zotuzwa"
  21,46,"Naho bokorwako n’igice gitoyi gusa c’ibihano vy’Umuremyi wawe, ntankeka bovuze bati:- ibi bihano vyacu mu vy’ukuri twebwe twarahemukiye imitima yacu"
  21,47,Natwe tuzo shiraho iminzani y’ukuri k’umusi w’imperuka n’umutima w’umuntu uwariwe wese ntuzo hemukirwa na gatoyi naho coba ico kintu gifise uburemere bw’igishishwa c’umutende tuzo bishikiriza natwe turahagije kuba abamenyi buguharura
  21,48,Mu vy’ukuri twarahaye intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) hamwe n’intumwa y’Imana Haruna (iii) igitabu gitandukanya n’umuco hamwe n’ubutumwa kubantu bagamburukira Imana y’abo y’ukuri
  21,49,"N’abatinya Umuremyi wabo mugihe biherereye, kandi bagatinya n’umusi w’imperuka"
  21,50,"N’iyi Qur’ani n’ubutumwa bwahezagiwe twamanuriye kuri wewe, mbega mwebwe murabuhakana"
  21,51,Mu vy’ukuri twarahaye intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii) uburongozi bwiwe kuva kera kandi twari tumuzi neza
  21,52,"Mugihe yabwira Se wiwe hamwe n’abantu biwe ati:- mbega aya masanamu mwicarirako imisi yose muyasenga"
  21,53,"Nabo bamwishura bati:- twebwe twasanze basogokuru bacu bayasenga"
  21,54,"Nawe abishura ati:- ntankeka mwebwe hamwe nabaso banyu mwari mubuzimire buri k’umugaragaro"
  21,55,"Nabo\tbamwishura\tbati:-\tmbega\twaje\tngaha\tufise\tamajambo\ty’ukuri canke uri mubantu bafyinata"
  21,56,"Nawe\tabishura\tati:-\tahubwo\tUmuremyi\twanyu\tn’urya\tmuremyi w’Amajuru n’Isi yayaremye, nanje ndi muvyabona vyemeza ibi vyose"
  21,57,Ndarahiye kw’izina ry’Imana yuko jewe nzoyagirira nabi aya masanamu yanyu nimwampa umugongo mugenda iyo mugenda